metadata.name: Christmas 2021 #1/15
metadata.description:
2021 has been a busy year for Meeko and I! 

I got to get back out to the West coast a few times for a backpacking trip in Yosemite as well as a Summer Tahoe trip.

I finally got to meet many people from our company in person as we did our first offsite together in Costa Rica. We also did a trip to NYC for an NFT conference.

Last but not least, Meeko and I bought a house in October! Meeko's pumped to have a yard finally and is making good use of it.

The house needs some work but it has a lot of potential and has been a fun project. The current plan is that my Sister and Brother-in-law will be moving into the other unit in March!

Here are a few pictures from the year: https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1788bf6amTMuqBnQ6YYhlJOk0eSBKx008?usp=sharing

With Love,  
Nathan
